00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
(Watch on KonFlix.vip)

1
00:00:04,604 --> 00:00:06,439
The Xing Dynasty is
powerful and prosperous.

2
00:00:07,107 --> 00:00:09,627
It has been dominant in the Central Plains
for a hundred years.

3
00:00:09,876 --> 00:00:13,512
The northern Khan Su He of the Talhan

4
00:00:13,513 --> 00:00:17,016
led his fierce and warlike tribesmen to
repeatedly invade the border.

5
00:00:19,452 --> 00:00:23,132
The fifth prince of Xing Dynasty, Yin Qi, was
ordered by the emperor to quell the rebellion.

6
00:00:24,190 --> 00:00:25,225
Three years later,

7
00:00:25,592 --> 00:00:27,360
the border regions returned to peace.

8
00:00:28,395 --> 00:00:29,395
However.

9
00:00:29,462 --> 00:00:31,064
Su He's ambition remained unabated.

10
00:00:31,498 --> 00:00:34,234
He conspired with Yin Zhou,
the eldest prince of the Xing Dynasty.

11
00:00:34,667 --> 00:00:36,436
He intended to usurp the throne.

12
00:00:37,003 --> 00:00:38,671
And overthrow the government.

13
00:00:43,510 --> 00:00:44,711
The fifth prince arrives

14
00:00:44,911 --> 00:00:46,045
to meet the emperor.

15
00:00:46,179 --> 00:00:47,781
Who dares to stop us?

16
00:00:48,281 --> 00:00:50,215
We've been ordered by Prince Fengsun

17
00:00:50,216 --> 00:00:51,785
to take your lives here.

18
00:00:57,290 --> 00:00:58,191
Fellow soldiers,

19
00:00:58,291 --> 00:00:59,592
follow me to kill the traitors.

20
00:01:00,226 --> 00:01:01,394
And rescue the emperor!

21
00:01:24,751 --> 00:01:25,552
Your Highness

22
00:01:25,652 --> 00:01:26,652
Khan.

23
00:01:26,853 --> 00:01:29,756
Yin Qi has indeed returned with a troop.

24
00:01:30,023 --> 00:01:31,343
He is outside the imperial palace

25
00:01:31,524 --> 00:01:33,226
fighting with Khan's men.

26
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:37,430
It seems he will break into
the imperial palace soon.

27
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:43,103
To His Royal Highness, the Crown Prince.

28
00:01:43,503 --> 00:01:44,503
No.

29
00:01:44,604 --> 00:01:48,808
It should be the future Emperor of Daxing.

30
00:01:51,044 --> 00:01:52,645
This night's drama.

31
00:01:53,112 --> 00:01:56,115
I have been waiting for a long time.

32
00:02:04,858 --> 00:02:06,793
What a pity for your nephew.

33
00:02:07,093 --> 00:02:08,328
He has always believed

34
00:02:08,995 --> 00:02:11,164
that I would spare him and Yin Qi.

35
00:02:11,698 --> 00:02:12,698
Little does he know

36
00:02:13,032 --> 00:02:15,201
that he is just my hunter.

37
00:02:15,668 --> 00:02:17,504
Once he has hunted Yin Qi for me.

38
00:02:18,304 --> 00:02:19,973
I will grant his wish

39
00:02:20,540 --> 00:02:23,176
and send him and Yin Qi
to the netherworld together.

40
00:02:24,844 --> 00:02:26,579
I have heard long ago

41
00:02:28,248 --> 00:02:31,985
that your fifth younger brother has been
close friends with my nephew for many years.

42
00:02:33,152 --> 00:02:38,825
Will he really turn against my
nephew because of a forged letter?

43
00:02:41,361 --> 00:02:44,097
Being betrayed by someone you've been
with day and night for years

44
00:02:44,964 --> 00:02:46,633
is not a pleasant feeling.

45
00:02:49,068 --> 00:02:52,038
I want to see Yin Qi lose everything
with my own eyes.

46
00:02:52,906 --> 00:02:57,176
To kill the only person in this world who
still cares about himwith my own hands.

47
00:03:00,573 --> 00:03:02,308
Such a wonderful drama

48
00:03:02,916 --> 00:03:05,084
deserves such fine wine indeed.

49
00:03:06,286 --> 00:03:08,388
It's time for him to make an appearance.

50
00:03:13,993 --> 00:03:16,038
The Emperor was clearly
in the secret chamber we arranged.

51
00:03:16,062 --> 00:03:17,063
How could he be gone?

52
00:03:17,363 --> 00:03:18,498
Hurry up and find him!

53
00:03:29,709 --> 00:03:30,910
No need to search.

54
00:03:31,778 --> 00:03:33,580
We've already

55
00:03:34,347 --> 00:03:35,347
killed the old Emperor.

56
00:03:35,715 --> 00:03:37,183
How dare you disobey my orders?

57
00:03:37,951 --> 00:03:38,952
Act on your own accord.

58
00:03:39,752 --> 00:03:40,752
Fengsun.

59
00:03:40,987 --> 00:03:43,488
Do you really think the Khan would entrust

60
00:03:43,489 --> 00:03:44,489
the old Emperor's life

61
00:03:44,991 --> 00:03:46,492
into your hands?

62
00:03:47,827 --> 00:03:49,907
Hand over the Talhan's
military talisman obediently.

63
00:03:50,797 --> 00:03:53,566
The Khan might spare you
out of respect for your father

64
00:03:54,267 --> 00:03:55,501
and not kill you.

65
00:03:56,202 --> 00:03:59,505
It's not for you to demand
the talisman from me.

66
00:04:00,707 --> 00:04:02,041
Where are Su He and Yin Zhou?

67
00:04:02,175 --> 00:04:03,176
I want to see them.

68
00:04:08,414 --> 00:04:10,416
His life belongs to me.

69
00:04:11,017 --> 00:04:11,818
Qi.

70
00:04:11,951 --> 00:04:12,952
Why are you here?

71
00:04:18,173 --> 00:04:19,153
[Letter indicating plans to
kill the emperor in five days]

72
00:04:19,192 --> 00:04:21,160
If I hadn't obtained this secret letter.

73
00:04:22,629 --> 00:04:24,564
I wouldn't have seen your true colors.

74
00:04:25,231 --> 00:04:26,566
Hand over the talisman first.

75
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:29,035
Then I'll send you both to hell.

76
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:44,950
Qi.

77
00:04:48,655 --> 00:04:49,655
Pei Yanzhi.

78
00:04:50,089 --> 00:04:50,890
No

79
00:04:51,057 --> 00:04:52,097
I should call you Fengsun.

80
00:04:53,393 --> 00:04:54,627
The person I trusted most

81
00:04:54,794 --> 00:04:56,462
turned out to be a spy sent by Talhan.

82
00:04:56,829 --> 00:04:57,829
Today

83
00:04:57,897 --> 00:04:59,499
I will kill you with my own hands.

84
00:05:08,508 --> 00:05:09,508
What?

85
00:05:09,609 --> 00:05:10,410
Do it!

86
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:11,210
Qi.

87
00:05:11,210 --> 00:05:11,844
Leave here quickly

88
00:05:11,845 --> 00:05:13,489
I'll explain everything
to you after tonight.

89
00:05:13,513 --> 00:05:14,314
But right now.

90
00:05:14,414 --> 00:05:16,094
If you don't leave now, it'll be too late.

91
00:05:22,822 --> 00:05:27,760
Yin Qi, the fifth prince of Xing Dynasty,
colluded with the hostage Fengsun

92
00:05:28,777 --> 00:05:31,237
intending to usurp the throne.

93
00:05:31,631 --> 00:05:35,435
By [planning to] assassinate the
Emperor at the Southern Palace.

94
00:05:36,035 --> 00:05:37,035
Fortunately,

95
00:05:37,570 --> 00:05:38,570
the Crown Prince

96
00:05:38,938 --> 00:05:40,173
risked his life

97
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:42,041
to rescue the Emperor

98
00:05:43,609 --> 00:05:45,645
and slew the two traitors.

99
00:05:47,647 --> 00:05:51,484
This drama of failing to protect the king,

100
00:05:52,885 --> 00:05:54,187
killing the traitors,

101
00:05:55,154 --> 00:05:57,023
and ascending to the throne

102
00:05:58,291 --> 00:05:59,625
is truly splendid.

103
00:06:01,374 --> 00:06:03,876
I haven't been able to kill
him in these three years.

104
00:06:04,964 --> 00:06:10,169
If I hadn't lured him back using Pei Yanzhi
and eliminated him in one fell swoop,

105
00:06:11,637 --> 00:06:12,705
he would have

106
00:06:13,506 --> 00:06:14,946
become a major threat in the future.

107
00:06:56,649 --> 00:06:58,017
I thought

108
00:06:59,418 --> 00:07:03,189
going to the border would
bring peace to the realm.

109
00:07:04,690 --> 00:07:05,690
Yet I didn't expect,

110
00:07:07,673 --> 00:07:08,941
in just three years,

111
00:07:10,029 --> 00:07:11,297
upon my return,

112
00:07:11,864 --> 00:07:14,434
I didn't even get to see
my father's face one last time.

113
00:07:16,803 --> 00:07:20,840
My best friend became a traitor for Daxing.

114
00:07:22,308 --> 00:07:23,576
My brother

115
00:07:24,410 --> 00:07:26,012
killed his own brother and father.

116
00:07:31,551 --> 00:07:32,551
Yin Zhou,

117
00:07:33,853 --> 00:07:35,955
can you sit on this throne

118
00:07:37,089 --> 00:07:38,791
stained with blood in peace?

119
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:58,277
Your skills in archery come
from me and my teaching.

120
00:07:58,611 --> 00:08:01,848
Let me see how well you've learned.

121
00:08:34,313 --> 00:08:35,548
Qi.

122
00:08:36,148 --> 00:08:37,148
Qi.

123
00:08:38,985 --> 00:08:39,985
Qi.

124
00:08:56,702 --> 00:08:57,702
Qi.

125
00:08:58,304 --> 00:08:59,105
Hurry up.

126
00:08:59,106 --> 00:09:01,807
Colorful sleeves eagerly hold jade cups.

127
00:09:01,908 --> 00:09:05,778
See how rosy-cheeked we
were in our drunken revelry.

128
00:09:07,213 --> 00:09:09,333
Dancing until the moon
sinks behind the willow trees.

129
00:09:09,815 --> 00:09:12,885
Singing until the wind fades beneath
the peach blossom fans.

130
00:09:13,886 --> 00:09:14,954
Since our parting,

131
00:09:15,555 --> 00:09:16,756
I recall our meetings,

132
00:09:17,223 --> 00:09:20,293
dreaming of you countless times.

133
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:24,297
Tonight, I hold up the silver lamp,

134
00:09:25,164 --> 00:09:31,037
fearing our meeting is but a dream.

135
00:10:47,413 --> 00:10:48,247
Let me see

136
00:10:48,248 --> 00:10:49,882
what you're wearing around your neck.

137
00:10:50,916 --> 00:10:52,618
You can't touch this wolf tooth pendant.

138
00:10:53,586 --> 00:10:55,453
This is a keepsake from
the White-Eyed Wolf King

139
00:10:55,454 --> 00:10:57,289
for his beloved.

140
00:10:57,823 --> 00:10:59,392
It can bless two lovers to

141
00:10:59,425 --> 00:11:01,093
be together for all eternity.

142
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:31,500
"Journey With You"

143
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:34,500
(Episode 1)

144
00:12:38,924 --> 00:12:40,284
Has His Highness not awakened yet?

145
00:12:40,826 --> 00:12:41,826
Not yet,

146
00:12:42,061 --> 00:12:42,728
but don't worry,

147
00:12:42,728 --> 00:12:43,728
I'm here.

148
00:13:08,587 --> 00:13:09,588
This is Yonghe Palace,

149
00:13:10,222 --> 00:13:11,524
I'm not dead.

150
00:13:12,024 --> 00:13:12,725
No,

151
00:13:12,725 --> 00:13:13,725
this can't be.

152
00:13:14,727 --> 00:13:17,496
That arrow clearly hit me in the chest.

153
00:13:18,264 --> 00:13:19,698
What on earth is going on?

154
00:13:25,604 --> 00:13:26,604
Qi,

155
00:13:27,039 --> 00:13:28,107
you've finally awakened.

156
00:13:28,207 --> 00:13:29,207
You,

157
00:13:29,675 --> 00:13:30,675
don't touch me.

158
00:13:31,043 --> 00:13:31,844
Pei Yanzhi,

159
00:13:31,977 --> 00:13:33,012
you traitor.

160
00:13:34,446 --> 00:13:35,247
Qi,

161
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:36,674
you're confused from your illness.

162
00:13:41,620 --> 00:13:42,421
Today,

163
00:13:42,588 --> 00:13:43,621
I must kill you

164
00:13:43,622 --> 00:13:44,723
to avenge my father.

165
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:52,030
Qi,

166
00:13:53,199 --> 00:13:54,400
what's wrong with you?

167
00:14:08,981 --> 00:14:09,981
Thank goodness,

168
00:14:10,015 --> 00:14:11,584
Your Highness has finally awakened.

169
00:14:12,097 --> 00:14:13,264
Do you feel better?

170
00:14:19,859 --> 00:14:20,793
The fever has subsided,

171
00:14:20,826 --> 00:14:22,528
but it worried me greatly.

172
00:14:22,728 --> 00:14:24,229
Just now, the Imperial Concubine asked me

173
00:14:24,230 --> 00:14:25,430
if Your Highness had awakened.

174
00:14:26,632 --> 00:14:27,632
What did you say?

175
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,200
My mother,

176
00:14:29,802 --> 00:14:30,802
she's still alive?

177
00:14:32,805 --> 00:14:34,305
Your Highness must be confused from sleep

178
00:14:34,306 --> 00:14:35,674
to say such nonsense.

179
00:14:37,376 --> 00:14:38,376
Qi,

180
00:14:41,714 --> 00:14:42,715
Mother is seriously ill,

181
00:14:43,215 --> 00:14:44,817
I've returned to three years ago.

182
00:14:51,924 --> 00:14:53,050
Brother, you've awakened.

183
00:14:53,197 --> 00:14:55,894
Heshu, you're here too.

184
00:14:57,663 --> 00:14:58,663
That's good,

185
00:14:59,598 --> 00:15:00,598
that's good.

186
00:15:01,533 --> 00:15:03,235
Where else would I be if not here?

187
00:15:04,003 --> 00:15:04,903
Since you've awakened,

188
00:15:04,904 --> 00:15:06,705
come with me to visit Mother quickly.

189
00:15:08,841 --> 00:15:09,975
What's wrong with you?

190
00:15:10,309 --> 00:15:11,477
Are you feeling unwell?

191
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:12,990
Should I call the imperial physician?

192
00:15:15,614 --> 00:15:16,415
Heshu,

193
00:15:16,482 --> 00:15:17,482
I'm fine.

194
00:15:17,683 --> 00:15:18,450
Come,

195
00:15:18,451 --> 00:15:19,718
let's go visit Mother quickly.

196
00:15:39,271 --> 00:15:40,271
Mother.

197
00:15:53,319 --> 00:15:54,319
Mother.

198
00:15:55,287 --> 00:15:56,287
Qi,

199
00:15:56,989 --> 00:15:58,257
you've awakened,

200
00:15:58,691 --> 00:16:00,526
I can rest easy now.

201
00:16:02,494 --> 00:16:03,494
Mother

202
00:16:06,865 --> 00:16:08,334
why are you crying again?

203
00:16:08,934 --> 00:16:10,836
A man doesn't shed tears easily.

204
00:16:12,604 --> 00:16:13,939
Mother.

205
00:16:16,308 --> 00:16:18,210
I just miss you so much.

206
00:16:20,279 --> 00:16:22,214
I really miss you.

207
00:16:24,984 --> 00:16:25,984
You,

208
00:16:26,585 --> 00:16:28,053
still such a child.

209
00:16:40,099 --> 00:16:41,099
Heshu,

210
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,434
what day is it today?

211
00:16:42,534 --> 00:16:43,934
The tenth day of the seventh month.

212
00:16:44,236 --> 00:16:45,236
Your Highness,

213
00:16:45,504 --> 00:16:47,039
how could you forget this?

214
00:16:47,272 --> 00:16:48,632
The tenth day of the seventh month

215
00:16:49,274 --> 00:16:51,110
is the day before Mother passed away.

216
00:16:53,512 --> 00:16:55,214
Mother can't keep coughing like this.

217
00:16:55,581 --> 00:16:56,081
Brother,

218
00:16:56,082 --> 00:16:57,483
let's go ask Father.

219
00:16:57,616 --> 00:16:58,851
He loves Mother so much,

220
00:16:58,917 --> 00:17:00,829
he'll surely find the best
doctors in the land for her.

221
00:17:00,853 --> 00:17:03,655
Maybe then Mother's illness will be cured.

222
00:17:03,989 --> 00:17:05,057
Don't go,

223
00:17:05,657 --> 00:17:06,657
Heshu.

224
00:17:07,092 --> 00:17:08,092
Qi.

225
00:17:09,094 --> 00:17:10,996
Mother doesn't have much time left.

226
00:17:11,230 --> 00:17:13,332
You must stay and keep me company.

227
00:17:13,799 --> 00:17:15,234
Mother, don't say that.

228
00:17:16,422 --> 00:17:19,425
I know what kind of state I'm in.

229
00:17:20,606 --> 00:17:24,810
I don't want to face him at this time.

230
00:17:26,412 --> 00:17:28,847
As long as you're by Mother's side,

231
00:17:30,015 --> 00:17:32,117
I'll be content.

232
00:17:38,023 --> 00:17:39,425
Brother, brother!

233
00:17:41,794 --> 00:17:42,794
Your Highness.

234
00:17:47,266 --> 00:17:49,034
Why did you make me come back on this day?

235
00:17:49,661 --> 00:17:52,062
Why couldn't I have stayed with Mother
for a few more days?

236
00:17:52,204 --> 00:17:54,073
Why couldn't you give me more time?

237
00:17:55,007 --> 00:17:56,007
Maybe then.

238
00:17:56,375 --> 00:17:57,843
Mother wouldn't have died.

239
00:17:59,378 --> 00:18:00,378
Qi,

240
00:18:06,051 --> 00:18:07,051
Qi,

241
00:18:15,594 --> 00:18:16,594
Qi

242
00:18:16,628 --> 00:18:18,997
I know you're hurting,

243
00:18:19,198 --> 00:18:20,899
but you can't hurt yourself like this.

244
00:18:23,202 --> 00:18:24,703
If you need to vent,

245
00:18:25,304 --> 00:18:26,805
punch me instead.

246
00:18:35,914 --> 00:18:37,115
Your Highness, Your Highness,

247
00:18:37,583 --> 00:18:38,583
something's wrong.

248
00:18:39,384 --> 00:18:40,519
The Crown Prince has

249
00:18:40,786 --> 00:18:42,888
suddenly come to visit Concubine Chen.

250
00:18:46,825 --> 00:18:48,627
Almost done, wait a moment.

251
00:18:48,894 --> 00:18:51,797
The Crown Prince arrives.

252
00:18:56,468 --> 00:18:57,669
Mother is unwell,

253
00:18:57,722 --> 00:18:59,590
and I must attend to her.
I can't entertain guests.

254
00:18:59,805 --> 00:19:01,605
Brother, you've come
at an inconvenient time.

255
00:19:01,673 --> 00:19:02,941
Please leave.

256
00:19:03,108 --> 00:19:04,108
Heshu,

257
00:19:09,982 --> 00:19:12,284
it's precisely because
Concubine Chen is seriously ill

258
00:19:12,684 --> 00:19:14,853
that I've come on behalf
of the Empress to visit her.

259
00:19:15,854 --> 00:19:17,855
I'm afraid it will disappoint Brother.

260
00:19:17,856 --> 00:19:19,625
My mother is still alive and well.

261
00:19:19,725 --> 00:19:21,125
When she recovers in a few days,

262
00:19:21,126 --> 00:19:23,126
she'll personally pay her
respects to the Empress.

263
00:19:23,529 --> 00:19:24,730
Heshu, stop!

264
00:19:26,899 --> 00:19:29,735
How can you speak to
your elder brother like that?

265
00:19:32,404 --> 00:19:33,405
Heshu is right.

266
00:19:57,429 --> 00:19:59,298
Since Brother has already seen Mother,

267
00:19:59,598 --> 00:20:00,933
please leave now.

268
00:20:09,441 --> 00:20:13,912
Concubine Chen has truly
raised a fine daughter and son.

269
00:20:39,938 --> 00:20:41,006
Are you alright, Mother?

270
00:20:41,273 --> 00:20:43,175
Qi, Qi.

271
00:20:46,011 --> 00:20:47,011
Stop.

272
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:49,680
Come back with me.

273
00:20:56,588 --> 00:20:58,023
I advise you,

274
00:20:58,290 --> 00:20:59,891
while your mother is still alive,

275
00:20:59,925 --> 00:21:02,427
spend as much time with her as you can.

276
00:21:03,028 --> 00:21:05,030
When Concubine Chen passes away,

277
00:21:05,197 --> 00:21:08,133
you'll regret wasting
time arguing with me here.

278
00:21:08,333 --> 00:21:09,835
I also advise Brother,

279
00:21:10,602 --> 00:21:12,337
those who do evil will reap what they sow.

280
00:21:12,904 --> 00:21:16,041
One day, you'll face the
consequences of your actions.

281
00:21:16,775 --> 00:21:17,775
Yin Qi,

282
00:21:17,909 --> 00:21:20,178
how dare you speak to me like that!

283
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:23,248
When Concubine Chen dies,

284
00:21:23,582 --> 00:21:26,785
you, the Fifth Prince, will
surely be disliked by Father.

285
00:21:27,286 --> 00:21:30,589
Let's see if you dare
to be so arrogant then.

286
00:21:41,833 --> 00:21:42,833
Move aside!

287
00:21:43,068 --> 00:21:44,068
Your Highness,

288
00:21:44,136 --> 00:21:45,637
fighting with the Crown Prince

289
00:21:45,871 --> 00:21:47,606
in Concubine Chen's palace

290
00:21:47,939 --> 00:21:49,099
will surely anger the Emperor

291
00:21:49,341 --> 00:21:50,742
if he finds out.

292
00:21:52,044 --> 00:21:53,211
He's right.

293
00:21:53,512 --> 00:21:55,314
No one knows what I've been through.

294
00:21:55,781 --> 00:21:57,449
If others find out,

295
00:21:57,616 --> 00:21:58,696
it will only cause trouble.

296
00:21:59,685 --> 00:22:01,253
Now that I'm back,

297
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:04,222
I'm not afraid of finding a
chance to eliminate Yin Zhou.

298
00:22:06,925 --> 00:22:07,925
Qi,

299
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:09,828
put down the sword.

300
00:22:17,069 --> 00:22:17,369
Mother.

301
00:22:17,736 --> 00:22:18,736
Mother.

302
00:22:24,142 --> 00:22:26,078
After being by Yin Qi's side for so long,

303
00:22:26,578 --> 00:22:27,978
you really think

304
00:22:27,979 --> 00:22:29,881
you're a loyal guard?

305
00:22:41,793 --> 00:22:42,793
Mother

306
00:22:43,061 --> 00:22:45,141
why are you pretending to
be sick to scare your son?

307
00:22:49,835 --> 00:22:50,835
Heshu,

308
00:22:58,443 --> 00:23:01,046
Mother is worried that
you'll act impulsively and

309
00:23:01,279 --> 00:23:02,814
offend your elder brother.

310
00:23:04,049 --> 00:23:06,184
He's not someone you can afford to offend.

311
00:23:07,119 --> 00:23:10,055
Don't forget what happened to your third
and fourth elder brothers.

312
00:23:11,423 --> 00:23:12,424
Mother, don't worry.

313
00:23:12,991 --> 00:23:14,226
I know now.

314
00:23:15,260 --> 00:23:16,928
I'll be more careful in the future.

315
00:23:29,541 --> 00:23:30,541
Does it hurt?

316
00:23:33,845 --> 00:23:34,845
Mother, don't worry.

317
00:23:35,781 --> 00:23:37,048
I'm not hurt.

318
00:24:16,054 --> 00:24:17,054
Your Highness,

319
00:24:20,826 --> 00:24:21,626
Your Highness!

320
00:24:21,793 --> 00:24:23,595
You've lost a lot of weight recently.

321
00:24:23,795 --> 00:24:26,198
Please take care of yourself.

322
00:24:38,777 --> 00:24:39,777
Duan Yi, Duan Yong!

323
00:24:40,091 --> 00:24:40,725
Yes?

324
00:24:40,979 --> 00:24:43,248
Find a way to investigate
Su He's information.

325
00:24:43,381 --> 00:24:44,449
The more, the better.

326
00:24:46,251 --> 00:24:47,251
Ziming,

327
00:24:47,986 --> 00:24:50,255
keep an eye on every move
in Mingde Palace for me.

328
00:24:51,189 --> 00:24:52,189
Mingde Palace.

329
00:24:52,490 --> 00:24:54,793
The Crown Prince has always
been somewhat overbearing.

330
00:24:54,926 --> 00:24:56,846
But you've never cared
about such things before.

331
00:24:57,095 --> 00:24:58,095
Why suddenly?

332
00:24:58,129 --> 00:24:58,930
Yes.

333
00:24:59,130 --> 00:25:00,130
Your Highness.

334
00:25:00,632 --> 00:25:02,400
Su He is the uncle of Prince Pei.

335
00:25:02,934 --> 00:25:04,694
If Your Highness wants
to investigate Su He,

336
00:25:04,903 --> 00:25:06,904
why not just ask Pei directly?

337
00:25:06,905 --> 00:25:08,025
Don't ask so many questions.

338
00:25:08,540 --> 00:25:10,008
Just do as I say.

339
00:25:10,842 --> 00:25:11,882
Your Highness, forgive me.

340
00:25:12,244 --> 00:25:13,778
I will do my utmost.

341
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:16,080
By the way,

342
00:25:16,915 --> 00:25:18,315
help me prepare more ice
containers and agarwood

343
00:25:18,316 --> 00:25:19,818
outside the palace

344
00:25:20,051 --> 00:25:21,286
in case of necessity.

345
00:25:22,287 --> 00:25:23,287
Ice containers?

346
00:25:26,625 --> 00:25:28,126
Just do as I say.

347
00:25:28,894 --> 00:25:29,995
Understood, Your Highness.

348
00:25:57,622 --> 00:25:59,791
What's wrong with you today?

349
00:26:00,792 --> 00:26:03,628
In the past, when Yin Zhou
showed off in front of you,

350
00:26:04,462 --> 00:26:05,931
you just laughed it off.

351
00:26:06,865 --> 00:26:08,705
This doesn't seem like
something you would do.

352
00:26:11,503 --> 00:26:13,223
Do you care a lot about your elder brother?

353
00:26:16,708 --> 00:26:17,988
Concubine Chen is seriously ill,

354
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:20,445
and many eyes are watching Yunhe Palace.

355
00:26:22,447 --> 00:26:25,784
I know you feel it's unfair
for Concubine Chen.

356
00:26:27,052 --> 00:26:28,186
But Qi, no one knows

357
00:26:29,521 --> 00:26:32,256
what will happen

358
00:26:32,257 --> 00:26:34,526
if these words reach the Emperor's ears.

359
00:26:35,093 --> 00:26:37,796
What I care about is you.

360
00:26:52,711 --> 00:26:54,379
Why are you being so nice to me now?

361
00:26:56,481 --> 00:26:57,849
Why are you asking this suddenly?

362
00:27:03,054 --> 00:27:04,222
If one day,

363
00:27:04,990 --> 00:27:07,525
we have to stand on opposite sides,

364
00:27:08,126 --> 00:27:09,126
Then we'll

365
00:27:09,894 --> 00:27:11,396
face each other with swords,

366
00:27:11,496 --> 00:27:12,664
fighting to the death.

367
00:27:14,432 --> 00:27:15,432
If at that time,

368
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:16,877
I recall

369
00:27:16,902 --> 00:27:18,403
your care for me today,

370
00:27:19,437 --> 00:27:21,272
What kind of feelings will I have?

371
00:27:30,508 --> 00:27:33,068
You must be exhausted from
taking care of Concubine Chen lately,

372
00:27:33,184 --> 00:27:35,465
that's why Your Highness is
having such strange thoughts.

373
00:27:35,787 --> 00:27:36,788
It's late, Your Highness.

374
00:27:37,389 --> 00:27:38,490
Please rest early.

375
00:27:42,661 --> 00:27:45,030
It's precisely because
you're treating me so well now

376
00:27:45,630 --> 00:27:46,898
that I can't believe

377
00:27:47,365 --> 00:27:48,999
that the "you" who wanted
to kill me in my past life

378
00:27:49,024 --> 00:27:50,959
is the same person standing before me now.

379
00:27:52,137 --> 00:27:54,539
Since Heaven has given
me a chance to live again,

380
00:27:55,140 --> 00:27:56,140
This time,

381
00:27:56,574 --> 00:27:58,410
I must change our fate.

382
00:27:58,476 --> 00:27:59,811
Your Highness, Your Highness.

383
00:28:00,078 --> 00:28:01,446
Concubine Chen is not doing well.

384
00:28:10,188 --> 00:28:11,188
Mother.

385
00:28:14,692 --> 00:28:15,692
Heshu,

386
00:28:16,728 --> 00:28:18,096
don't be sad.

387
00:28:20,198 --> 00:28:23,301
After being trapped in this
palace for so many years,

388
00:28:24,469 --> 00:28:26,805
I can finally leave now.

389
00:28:27,639 --> 00:28:29,474
You should be happy for me.

390
00:28:30,875 --> 00:28:31,676
Mother,

391
00:28:31,810 --> 00:28:32,977
don't worry.

392
00:28:33,511 --> 00:28:34,579
I won't cry.

393
00:28:45,824 --> 00:28:46,824
Your Highness,

394
00:28:46,849 --> 00:28:48,192
[Since we've parted, I've
longed to meet you again;

395
00:28:48,217 --> 00:28:50,872
how many times have my soul and
dreams journeyed with you?]

396
00:28:58,303 --> 00:28:59,303
Qi.

397
00:29:00,205 --> 00:29:04,676
Let this strand of hair be
buried in Jiangnan for me,

398
00:29:06,277 --> 00:29:09,080
so that my soul can return to my hometown.

399
00:29:11,883 --> 00:29:14,152
In all my future lives,

400
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:16,588
I never want

401
00:29:16,589 --> 00:29:18,056
to have any connection

402
00:29:19,557 --> 00:29:21,226
with the royal family again.

403
00:29:32,337 --> 00:29:33,337
Mother.

404
00:29:33,671 --> 00:29:34,205
Concubine.

405
00:29:34,205 --> 00:29:34,439
Mother.

406
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:35,907
Don't leave me.

407
00:29:36,474 --> 00:29:37,474
Mother.

408
00:29:38,610 --> 00:29:40,712
Don't leave me and my elder brother.

409
00:29:40,879 --> 00:29:41,879
Mother.

410
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:56,460
Concubine Chen.

411
00:29:57,862 --> 00:29:58,997
May you rest in peace.

412
00:30:03,802 --> 00:30:04,802
Mother.

413
00:30:07,005 --> 00:30:08,907
Your son knows what to do now.

414
00:30:33,698 --> 00:30:35,400
The Virtuous Concubine Su,

415
00:30:36,234 --> 00:30:37,735
the vastness of heaven,

416
00:30:38,636 --> 00:30:40,505
may your soul return.

417
00:30:44,442 --> 00:30:46,010
The Virtuous Concubine Su,

418
00:30:47,178 --> 00:30:48,880
the vastness of heaven,

419
00:30:50,248 --> 00:30:52,584
may your soul return.

420
00:30:57,922 --> 00:30:59,657
The Virtuous Concubine Su,

421
00:31:00,792 --> 00:31:02,527
the vastness of heaven,

422
00:31:04,195 --> 00:31:06,431
may your soul return.

423
00:31:12,670 --> 00:31:13,670
Mother.

424
00:31:16,741 --> 00:31:17,741
Elder brother.

425
00:31:18,309 --> 00:31:20,211
Why don't we ask Father for mercy

426
00:31:20,411 --> 00:31:22,714
and have Mother's
coffin buried in Jiangnan?

427
00:31:23,581 --> 00:31:24,916
It's not appropriate.

428
00:31:25,450 --> 00:31:26,718
Father won't agree.

429
00:31:27,285 --> 00:31:28,285
For Mother's sake,

430
00:31:28,419 --> 00:31:29,520
we should at least try.

431
00:31:31,589 --> 00:31:32,589
Anyway,

432
00:31:32,857 --> 00:31:34,859
in front of Father and the Empress,

433
00:31:35,627 --> 00:31:37,328
do not mention this under any circumstance.

434
00:31:47,238 --> 00:31:48,238
Nanny Su,

435
00:31:48,439 --> 00:31:50,141
why only this one container of ice?

436
00:31:50,275 --> 00:31:51,275
This won't be enough.

437
00:31:51,442 --> 00:31:53,187
Just now, when I went to the
Inner Servants Department,

438
00:31:53,211 --> 00:31:54,379
I was deliberately hindered.

439
00:31:54,479 --> 00:31:55,446
It's so hot,

440
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:56,481
and Concubine might...

441
00:31:57,682 --> 00:31:59,317
These heartless servants!

442
00:32:00,518 --> 00:32:02,358
They must have been
instigated by the Empress.

443
00:32:02,387 --> 00:32:03,867
Only then would they dare to do this.

444
00:32:04,522 --> 00:32:05,723
If they won't give it,

445
00:32:05,890 --> 00:32:07,292
I'll go get it myself.

446
00:32:09,294 --> 00:32:10,294
Heshu.

447
00:32:10,595 --> 00:32:11,396
Don't do anything

448
00:32:11,397 --> 00:32:12,897
that would upset Mother today.

449
00:32:13,197 --> 00:32:14,198
I have a way.

450
00:32:25,910 --> 00:32:26,910
Your Highness,

451
00:32:27,879 --> 00:32:28,979
Bring

452
00:32:28,980 --> 00:32:30,124
the ice containers and agarwood

453
00:32:30,148 --> 00:32:31,316
I told you to prepare.

454
00:32:31,616 --> 00:32:33,051
Your Highness is truly prescient.

455
00:32:33,685 --> 00:32:34,485
Hurry.

456
00:32:34,652 --> 00:32:35,453
Qi.

457
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:36,520
Don't go.

458
00:32:36,688 --> 00:32:38,408
The ice containers and agarwood you wanted,

459
00:32:38,456 --> 00:32:39,976
I've already sent someone to buy them.

460
00:32:50,101 --> 00:32:51,135
These ice containers,

461
00:32:51,803 --> 00:32:55,431
even with money, we couldn't have bought
so many in such a short amount of time.

462
00:32:55,840 --> 00:32:58,476
Could it be that you knew in advance

463
00:32:58,876 --> 00:33:01,245
that Mother would be hindered?

464
00:33:02,513 --> 00:33:03,513
Concubine Chen,

465
00:33:04,115 --> 00:33:06,517
has been deliberately
hindered ever since she fell ill.

466
00:33:07,618 --> 00:33:08,618
Just in case,

467
00:33:08,619 --> 00:33:10,388
I prepared these in advance.

468
00:33:11,189 --> 00:33:12,457
I just didn't expect

469
00:33:12,790 --> 00:33:14,792
that you would think of it too.

470
00:33:16,386 --> 00:33:19,156
Did you think I'll be like Heshu,

471
00:33:19,797 --> 00:33:22,033
drowning in grief over losing Mother?

472
00:33:26,004 --> 00:33:27,071
Mother is gone,

473
00:33:27,498 --> 00:33:29,300
I have to be Heshu's pillar of strength.

474
00:33:30,641 --> 00:33:32,176
These preemptive measures,

475
00:33:32,410 --> 00:33:33,778
are what I should do.

476
00:33:46,717 --> 00:33:49,487
I've definitely seen
this emblem in my past life.

477
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:50,660
Fifth Prince,

478
00:33:51,129 --> 00:33:52,063
are you alright?

479
00:33:52,063 --> 00:33:53,063
It's nothing.

480
00:34:19,090 --> 00:34:21,592
I've already ordered the royal mausoleum
to be renovated.

481
00:34:22,393 --> 00:34:23,713
After the funeral rites are over,

482
00:34:24,195 --> 00:34:25,797
Concubine Chen will be sent there.

483
00:34:26,063 --> 00:34:28,265
It's also my last gift

484
00:34:28,266 --> 00:34:29,934
to my beloved concubine.

485
00:34:31,402 --> 00:34:34,705
Concubine Chen always said she
wanted to go back to Jiangnan to see it.

486
00:34:35,640 --> 00:34:36,641
In a while,

487
00:34:37,208 --> 00:34:38,409
I'll order someone to build

488
00:34:39,010 --> 00:34:40,878
a Jiangnan-style garden in the capital

489
00:34:41,212 --> 00:34:42,652
and bestow it upon you two siblings.

490
00:34:43,848 --> 00:34:44,649
Father,

491
00:34:44,682 --> 00:34:46,851
I have a request to ask of Father.

492
00:34:47,018 --> 00:34:47,585
Before Mother passed away,

493
00:34:47,585 --> 00:34:48,585
Heshu, be quiet.

494
00:34:53,624 --> 00:34:54,425
Heshu,

495
00:34:54,625 --> 00:34:55,927
what is your request?

496
00:34:56,294 --> 00:34:57,295
Speak freely.

497
00:34:57,395 --> 00:34:58,395
Father,

498
00:34:58,529 --> 00:34:59,664
Heshu means

499
00:34:59,730 --> 00:35:01,865
the palace gift is too much
for us two siblings to accept.

500
00:35:01,866 --> 00:35:03,067
We truly feel unworthy of it.

501
00:35:04,101 --> 00:35:05,679
We only hope Father
will grant us permission

502
00:35:05,703 --> 00:35:07,343
to accompany Mother on her final journey.

503
00:35:08,473 --> 00:35:09,707
I grant it.

504
00:35:22,987 --> 00:35:26,491
The Crown Prince has arrived.

505
00:35:30,294 --> 00:35:31,294
Qi.

506
00:35:31,829 --> 00:35:33,207
Yin Zhou is deliberately provoking us.

507
00:35:33,231 --> 00:35:34,065
Don't get excited.

508
00:35:34,066 --> 00:35:35,099
Don't fall into his trap.

509
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:37,400
Take it easy.

510
00:35:43,508 --> 00:35:45,018
The Imperial Concubine
Chen has passed away.

511
00:35:45,042 --> 00:35:47,078
Pei is also wearing mourning clothes.

512
00:35:47,478 --> 00:35:48,513
Those who don't know

513
00:35:48,779 --> 00:35:50,580
might even think you were
sent by the grassland tribes

514
00:35:50,581 --> 00:35:52,862
to form an alliance
with our Great Xing through marriage.

515
00:35:53,017 --> 00:35:54,017
What are you doing here?

516
00:35:55,072 --> 00:35:58,509
Naturally, I've come to pay my
respects to the Imperial Concubine Chen.

517
00:35:59,056 --> 00:35:59,891
Since it's a condolence visit,

518
00:35:59,924 --> 00:36:01,459
what's the meaning of you wearing red?

519
00:36:01,926 --> 00:36:02,660
Yin Zhou,

520
00:36:02,661 --> 00:36:03,861
don't do too much.

521
00:36:04,529 --> 00:36:05,730
A mere concubine,

522
00:36:05,997 --> 00:36:07,331
her death is nothing significant.

523
00:36:07,465 --> 00:36:08,099
Do you expect

524
00:36:08,100 --> 00:36:10,535
me to also wear mourning clothes?

525
00:36:10,701 --> 00:36:12,970
Isn't having Pei
wear them enough?

526
00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:14,714
I'll tell Father Emperor.

527
00:36:14,739 --> 00:36:16,507
See if you dare to be so arrogant then.

528
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:24,424
Now that the Imperial
Concubine Chen is dead,

529
00:36:24,448 --> 00:36:26,784
why are you still staying by
this useless person's side?

530
00:36:41,071 --> 00:36:46,118
[The character indicating
offerings to the deceased]

531
00:37:13,898 --> 00:37:14,898
Qi,

532
00:37:15,533 --> 00:37:17,493
Yin Zhou was just trying
to sow discord just now.

533
00:37:17,635 --> 00:37:19,036
I'm from your palace.

534
00:37:19,203 --> 00:37:20,237
I was before,

535
00:37:20,438 --> 00:37:21,606
and I will be in the future.

536
00:37:22,873 --> 00:37:24,273
People strive for higher positions.

537
00:37:26,244 --> 00:37:28,112
If you insist on going to Yin Zhou's side,

538
00:37:28,913 --> 00:37:30,314
how could I stop you?

539
00:37:37,054 --> 00:37:38,122
Qi,

540
00:37:39,924 --> 00:37:41,659
Are you hiding something from me?

541
00:37:48,866 --> 00:37:50,233
What could I possibly be hiding from you?

542
00:37:50,234 --> 00:37:51,502
I know you too well.

543
00:37:52,837 --> 00:37:54,438
If you didn't have other plans,

544
00:37:55,106 --> 00:37:57,017
you would have definitely
joined He Shu just now

545
00:37:57,041 --> 00:37:58,175
to plead with the Emperor

546
00:37:58,709 --> 00:38:00,549
for the Imperial Concubine
Chen's last wishes.

547
00:38:11,022 --> 00:38:12,022
As expected,

548
00:38:12,623 --> 00:38:14,392
nothing escapes your eyes.

549
00:38:15,326 --> 00:38:16,127
That's right.

550
00:38:16,327 --> 00:38:17,995
I've already planned it out.

551
00:38:18,529 --> 00:38:21,132
Tonight, I'll send my
mother out of the palace

552
00:38:21,932 --> 00:38:23,099
and then send her back to Jiangnan.

553
00:38:23,100 --> 00:38:24,100
No,

554
00:38:24,435 --> 00:38:25,669
that's too dangerous.

555
00:38:25,670 --> 00:38:26,304
What if you get caught...

556
00:38:26,305 --> 00:38:28,305
I will definitely fulfill
my mother's last wishes.

557
00:38:28,673 --> 00:38:29,673
As for this matter,

558
00:38:30,141 --> 00:38:31,461
you don't have to worry about it.

559
00:38:42,853 --> 00:38:44,973
Yin Qi has been acting
strangely these past two days.

560
00:38:45,523 --> 00:38:46,991
Go tell that person

561
00:38:47,291 --> 00:38:48,859
to keep a close eye on him.

562
00:38:50,061 --> 00:38:51,061
Yes.

563
00:38:59,904 --> 00:39:01,344
The Imperial Concubine Chen is dead.

564
00:39:01,706 --> 00:39:03,007
What are your plans?

565
00:39:07,211 --> 00:39:08,612
With such a good opportunity,

566
00:39:09,113 --> 00:39:10,514
if I were you,

567
00:39:10,681 --> 00:39:14,018
I would have already planned to
drive Yin Qi out of the palace.

568
00:39:14,418 --> 00:39:15,418
For all these years,

569
00:39:15,720 --> 00:39:17,420
Father Emperor has been
hinting to Mother Empress

570
00:39:17,421 --> 00:39:19,190
to pass the crown prince position to me.

571
00:39:19,423 --> 00:39:20,624
But what's the result?

572
00:39:21,225 --> 00:39:23,728
He still wants to use Yin
Qi to keep me in check.

573
00:39:24,729 --> 00:39:26,397
You're my son,

574
00:39:26,697 --> 00:39:29,200
the only legitimate son of Great Xing.

575
00:39:30,134 --> 00:39:32,803
You should naturally inherit the throne.

576
00:39:33,637 --> 00:39:35,206
If you had some skills,

577
00:39:35,539 --> 00:39:37,742
you would have already
become the crown prince by now.

578
00:39:38,075 --> 00:39:40,077
Why would I still need to plan for you?

579
00:39:40,845 --> 00:39:43,080
You really are so unpromising.

580
00:39:43,447 --> 00:39:45,415
I've already defeated the
third and fourth princes,

581
00:39:45,416 --> 00:39:46,984
driving them out of the palace.

582
00:39:49,186 --> 00:39:49,987
Yin Qi,

583
00:39:50,187 --> 00:39:51,621
He's just the son of a merchant,

584
00:39:51,622 --> 00:39:53,862
a lowly and stupid person
born to a merchant's daughter.

585
00:39:53,924 --> 00:39:55,191
Apart from reciting poems and painting,

586
00:39:55,192 --> 00:39:56,227
what else can he do?

587
00:39:56,460 --> 00:39:57,862
How dare he compete with me?

588
00:39:59,830 --> 00:40:01,441
He's just like the Imperial Concubine Chen,

589
00:40:01,465 --> 00:40:02,666
with just a pretty face.

590
00:40:02,833 --> 00:40:03,833
He...

591
00:40:11,208 --> 00:40:12,977
Fortunately, the heavens have eyes.

592
00:40:13,477 --> 00:40:14,477
This time,

593
00:40:14,979 --> 00:40:16,979
the Imperial Concubine
Chen died for a good cause.

594
00:40:18,048 --> 00:40:20,851
The favor she took from the Emperor,

595
00:40:22,052 --> 00:40:24,321
you must take it back from Yin Qi

596
00:40:24,855 --> 00:40:26,590
on my behalf.

597
00:40:34,532 --> 00:40:36,634
Don't let me down.

598
00:40:46,644 --> 00:40:50,915
Why does Your Highness look so preoccupied?

599
00:40:53,484 --> 00:40:56,187
Let this servant serve Your Highness well,

600
00:40:57,188 --> 00:41:00,124
and Your Highness
won't be troubled anymore.

601
00:41:22,313 --> 00:41:23,447
It's already night.

602
00:41:23,581 --> 00:41:24,648
Who's leaving the palace?

603
00:41:24,982 --> 00:41:25,982
This person,

604
00:41:26,450 --> 00:41:28,428
is our Fifth Prince who
wants to leave the palace.

605
00:41:28,452 --> 00:41:29,452
The Fifth Prince?

606
00:41:29,487 --> 00:41:30,487
Nonsense.

607
00:41:30,821 --> 00:41:33,524
He's supposed to escort the Imperial Concubine
Chen to the imperial mausoleum tomorrow morning.

608
00:41:33,991 --> 00:41:35,511
Why would he leave the palace tonight?

609
00:41:37,027 --> 00:41:37,828
What?

610
00:41:37,895 --> 00:41:39,063
Don't believe it's me?

611
00:41:41,465 --> 00:41:42,465
Fifth Prince.

612
00:41:42,666 --> 00:41:43,666
Are you letting him pass?

613
00:41:43,901 --> 00:41:44,901
Yes.

614
00:42:10,160 --> 00:42:11,160
Your Highness.

615
00:42:13,364 --> 00:42:14,364
Your Highness.

616
00:42:16,834 --> 00:42:17,834
Get lost.

617
00:42:23,207 --> 00:42:26,043
My fifth brother is being restless again.

